WEBVTT

00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:05.310
-ayter foroys mit undzer un- intervyu. mir haltn bay kaset numer fir

00:00:05.310 --> 00:00:07.710
bite, dertseyln vayter ayer

00:00:07.710 --> 00:00:08.960
iberlebung.

00:00:08.787 --> 00:00:09.793
ALSO

00:00:10.086 --> 00:00:13.936
yetst, farshteystu, in di geto ⟨iz aroysgekumen⟩ a bafel az me zol

00:00:13.936 --> 00:00:16.736
op- oproymen dem, EIN plats vos m'iz m-

00:00:16.736 --> 00:00:17.966
makhn far

00:00:17.966 --> 00:00:21.016
di apteylung far di ZIGEUNER lager.

00:00:21.016 --> 00:00:22.966
boy a ZIGEUNER lager.

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:26.773
hot men opge- opgerisn a teyl fun di geto

00:00:26.773 --> 00:00:30.023
dos iz gelign in, nisht vayt fun lebn dem shtroy RESORT

00:00:30.023 --> 00:00:31.882
un makhn a tsigayner lager.

00:00:31.939 --> 00:00:34.698
hot men arumgeringlt dem plats mit EIN parkn

00:00:34.698 --> 00:00:36.718
un di PAAR hayzer tsugenumen

00:00:36.718 --> 00:00:40.421
un dort hot men gebrengt arop, mentshn zenen gekumen tsu geyn ⟨ongetun⟩

00:00:40.421 --> 00:00:42.731
fayne HUTTEN mit federn

00:00:42.731 --> 00:00:46.952
kostyumen, elegant, mit KOFFERS mit kinder, elegant

00:00:47.042 --> 00:00:49.837
dos hot geheysn ⟨zenen⟩ tsigayner lager.

00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:52.800
m'hot dort arayngebrengt di mentshn.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:56.400
mir hobn tsugefirt mitn tramvay tsu do- dortn mentshn

00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:59.962
un dortn UNK ⟨hobn mir⟩ ayngeforn esn mit ⟨fayn⟩, ales tsunezamen.

00:01:00.205 --> 00:01:02.443
kurts tsu di zakh, ikh'l makhn kurts

00:01:02.685 --> 00:01:03.944
vos hot pasirt?

00:01:04.001 --> 00:01:06.308
dos iz nisht geven keyn tsigayner.

00:01:06.313 --> 00:01:07.505
dos iz gevezn

00:01:07.613 --> 00:01:13.634
inteligente mentshn vos zenen geven gegn, ⟨tsi⟩ sotsyalistn, ⟨azoyne⟩ mentshn vos zenen geven gegen dem rezhim.

00:01:13.634 --> 00:01:16.348
zey hobn tsuzamengenumen ⟨fun⟩ farshidene erter

00:01:16.810 --> 00:01:18.430
iz zeyer ⟨faynt⟩

00:01:18.430 --> 00:01:20.440
vayl a tsigayner ken men derkenen.

00:01:21.670 --> 00:01:26.288
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu, azoy hot zikh gefirt. in di geto iz gevezn, ikh hob geshpilt futbol

00:01:26.884 --> 00:01:31.755
hob ikh gehat ⟨FEUCHT⟩ iz geven a khaver fun di L.K.S., hot geshpilt in di L.K.S.

00:01:31.828 --> 00:01:35.720
er iz gevorn aza ⟨presiz⟩ vi ⟨SUTTER⟩ in di, in di

00:01:36.334 --> 00:01:37.543
KRIPO.

00:01:39.135 --> 00:01:41.350
mir hobn nisht getort, nor, ⟨veyst⟩ dokh

00:01:41.350 --> 00:01:43.900
er hot mir, un m'hot mikh, UNK ⟨nokh a molt⟩ geholfn.

00:01:45.092 --> 00:01:46.835
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu

00:01:46.835 --> 00:01:50.852
hobn zey ongehoybn tsu likvidirn di mentshn ⟨yeder⟩ tog

00:01:50.852 --> 00:01:52.359
hot men geshosn

00:01:52.450 --> 00:01:56.224
un m'hot ⟨UNK⟩gefirt. m'hot zey avekgefirt, ⟨m'iz tsugeforn⟩ in tramvay

00:01:57.242 --> 00:02:00.112
un avekgefir- avekgefirt keyn

00:02:00.112 --> 00:02:01.272
oyfn gutn ort aroys.

00:02:01.272 --> 00:02:04.692
nor dort hot men zey bagrobn, m'hot gemakht, undzere hobn gegrobn di UNK

00:02:04.692 --> 00:02:06.702
un zey zenen gekumen tsu forn mit di JEEPn

00:02:06.702 --> 00:02:08.659
un arumgeforn az me zol nisht UNK keyn s-

00:02:08.659 --> 00:02:10.349
s'zol nisht blaybn keyn SLAD.

00:02:10.523 --> 00:02:13.200
tsum letst iz gevezn, der tsveyter hot geheysn SCHMIDT.

00:02:13.797 --> 00:02:15.757
oykhet fun di KRIPO

00:02:15.757 --> 00:02:18.837
un dort, un dort UNK ⟨gebn⟩ arayn mit EIN hunt

00:02:18.837 --> 00:02:21.707
hot UNK epes UNK, un s'iz gevorn a tifus

00:02:21.707 --> 00:02:24.574
un der SCHMIDT iz geshtorbn. gepeygert.

00:02:24.647 --> 00:02:27.273
er iz geshtorbn, un dem hunt hot men geshosn.

00:02:27.398 --> 00:02:29.352
demolt UNK ongehoybn tsu likvidirn

00:02:29.352 --> 00:02:31.020
dem gantsn ZIGEUNER lager.

00:02:32.157 --> 00:02:34.448
fertik. mit eyn molt in di fri

00:02:34.448 --> 00:02:35.708
klingt men mir

00:02:35.708 --> 00:02:36.718
BIEBOW

00:02:36.718 --> 00:02:37.738
a bafel

00:02:37.738 --> 00:02:40.118
un er hot nisht geklungen, nor er git di bafel

00:02:40.118 --> 00:02:42.578
az ikh zol mir tsushteln oyfn BALUTER plats.

00:02:43.902 --> 00:02:48.621
⟨bin ikh opgeforn⟩ in BALUTER plats in di frimorgn, zogt er "forst arunter oyfn

00:02:48.897 --> 00:02:53.042
gutn ort," un mitgeshikt mir a yidishn politsyant.

00:02:53.588 --> 00:02:56.231
bin aruntergeforn in gutn ort tsum bagreber

00:02:56.389 --> 00:02:58.279
hot er gehat aroysgenumen d-

00:02:58.279 --> 00:03:02.899
a tog ⟨foroys⟩ hobn zey bagrobn mentshn, hobn zey bagrobn a kind ⟨vos iz⟩ efsher alt gevezn nayn yor oder tsen yor

00:03:02.899 --> 00:03:03.859
a meydele

00:03:05.468 --> 00:03:08.878
un der bagreber iz aroysgan in frimorgn. s'iz nisht geven ⟨gut⟩ UNK tsugemakht

00:03:08.878 --> 00:03:10.978
hot gehert krekhtsn, hot er geefnt

00:03:10.978 --> 00:03:12.128
un dos kind hot gelebt

00:03:12.128 --> 00:03:13.908
hot er zi aroysgenumen.

00:03:13.908 --> 00:03:15.635
⟨es⟩ zol onfirn tsum

00:03:15.635 --> 00:03:20.045
oyf, oyfn BALUTER plats mitn tramvay. bin ikh aruntergeforn oyfn BALUTER plats UNK tramvay mit dem

00:03:20.045 --> 00:03:21.335
mit dem politsyant

00:03:21.335 --> 00:03:22.623
un mit dem kind

00:03:24.655 --> 00:03:27.615
zenen mir ongekumen oyfn BALUTER plats, zenen mir araynganen mitn kind

00:03:27.615 --> 00:03:29.885
farshteystu, hot es getrogn dos kind, der

00:03:29.885 --> 00:03:30.892
politsyant

00:03:31.118 --> 00:03:33.958
hot es getrogn arayn UNK tsum, dort vu BIEBOW zitst

00:03:33.958 --> 00:03:35.718
hot er aroysgenumen dem revolver

00:03:35.718 --> 00:03:36.758
in mayne oygn

00:03:36.758 --> 00:03:38.268
⟨er hot im⟩ dershosn dos kind

00:03:38.268 --> 00:03:39.668
un forst tsurik mit dos.

00:03:39.668 --> 00:03:40.949
mot men es aruntergefirt

00:03:41.007 --> 00:03:42.720
tsurik dort. dos hob ikh gezen

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:43.864
dos ershte mol

00:03:43.864 --> 00:03:44.800
vi BIEBOW

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:45.658
hot geshosn.

00:03:46.542 --> 00:03:47.244
nu

00:03:47.453 --> 00:03:51.311
UNK vayter. heybt shoyn on vayter a, a groyse oyszidlung

00:03:51.756 --> 00:03:55.322
ahin shteyt men mit di tramvayen UNK khapn di mentshn aruntertsufirn

00:03:55.322 --> 00:03:56.761
a groyse oyszidlung

00:03:56.835 --> 00:03:59.235
shteyt bay rog FRANCISZKANA rog BRZEZINA

00:03:59.235 --> 00:04:00.655
shteyt der DAWID

00:04:00.655 --> 00:04:01.975
vos hot gearbet bay mir

00:04:01.975 --> 00:04:03.255
er hot gehat ongetun a hitl

00:04:03.255 --> 00:04:04.145
baym toyer

00:04:04.145 --> 00:04:07.263
UNK vart ⟨bay⟩ di zayt di tramvay nemt di mentshn UNK kumen

00:04:07.263 --> 00:04:10.526
iz gekumen ts- azoy vi BIEBOW iz ongekumen tsu geyn mit FUCHSn

00:04:10.526 --> 00:04:14.036
un ale hobn ongehoybn tsu loyfn, iz er arayngelofn in dem hoyz arayn ⟨oyfn⟩ hoyf UNK

00:04:14.036 --> 00:04:16.236
di parkn ⟨aroyf⟩ un iz aroyfgelofn ⟨in⟩ di tsveyte zayt.

00:04:16.236 --> 00:04:17.696
iz gekumen der BIEBOW

00:04:17.696 --> 00:04:19.876
zogt er "far vos hostu adurkhgelozt di mentshn?"

00:04:19.876 --> 00:04:22.693
ah un UNK ⟨koym⟩ er ruft ⟨zikh⟩ a mentshl a kleyns

00:04:22.693 --> 00:04:24.093
⟨iz⟩ geganen ⟨un⟩ m'hot im dershosn.

00:04:26.150 --> 00:04:28.727
nokh dem hot men aropgefirt UNK im oykhet oyfn gutn ort.

00:04:28.727 --> 00:04:31.267
hob ikh gezen shoyn dos tsveyte mol vi er hot geshosn.

00:04:32.037 --> 00:04:34.550
shpeter hot zikh ongehoybn di oyszidlung, di letste oyszidlung

00:04:34.550 --> 00:04:36.062
di, hot er gehaltn a rede

00:04:36.062 --> 00:04:38.442
ets geyts oyf arbet, un me likvidirt

00:04:39.342 --> 00:04:42.752
m'vet mitnemen ale mashinen, alts. m'hot ongehoybn tsu likvidirn

00:04:42.752 --> 00:04:45.532
ale mashinen, farshteystu, alts tsunezamen

00:04:45.532 --> 00:04:46.864
ongehoybn tsu likvidirn.

00:04:48.169 --> 00:04:49.732
me pakt mir alts.

00:04:49.772 --> 00:04:51.048
in di frimorgn

00:04:51.460 --> 00:04:53.620
finef a zeyger, dos shteyt geshribn

00:04:53.620 --> 00:04:55.650
kumt tsu forn der direktor SCHEIDT

00:04:55.650 --> 00:04:57.370
tsu mir oyf di linye

00:04:57.370 --> 00:04:59.570
un zogt tsu mir azoy. "KOPELMAN

00:04:59.570 --> 00:05:01.020
ICH VERABSCHIEDE MICH."

00:05:01.020 --> 00:05:03.637
er gezegnt zikh mit mir. er kumt shoyn nisht arayn

00:05:03.778 --> 00:05:05.403
in geto, er vet nisht kumen in geto arayn

00:05:05.403 --> 00:05:06.624
"nor kop HOCH

00:05:07.339 --> 00:05:09.392
MUT VERLOREN, ALLES VERLOREN.

00:05:09.668 --> 00:05:12.306
⟨tomer⟩ zolst nisht oyfgebn. dos gediert" zogt er "nisht lang."

00:05:12.306 --> 00:05:13.965
un ⟨MEIER⟩ shteyt dernebn

00:05:15.270 --> 00:05:20.427
un er VERSCHIEDET zikh un zogt tsu mir "kh- z- ⟨zol men⟩ haltn, vet men nisht ⟨farzukhn⟩," un dos dertseylt er mir den.

00:05:21.210 --> 00:05:22.604
dos iz gevezn

00:05:23.539 --> 00:05:24.545
fraytik

00:05:24.889 --> 00:05:26.047
iz dos gevezn.

00:05:26.998 --> 00:05:29.588
montik kumt tsu mir tsu geyn der mayster ⟨MEIER⟩

00:05:29.588 --> 00:05:31.008
un dertseylt mi- mir

00:05:31.008 --> 00:05:32.858
in zayt, keyner hert dos nisht

00:05:32.858 --> 00:05:34.868
az mir hobn shoyn nisht ⟨dem⟩ direktor SCHEIDT.

00:05:34.868 --> 00:05:36.248
vos hot pasirt?

00:05:37.090 --> 00:05:41.310
FUCHS iz gekumen tsu geyn, hot gezogt me z- muz bazaytikn di TRAMWAJARZn oykhet

00:05:41.310 --> 00:05:42.690
UNK tsu di oyszidlung.

00:05:42.793 --> 00:05:45.909
hot er gezogt "mayne TRAMWAJARZn vestu nisht rirn."

00:05:47.080 --> 00:05:50.310
er hot ⟨zikh ongehoybn⟩ tsu tsanken. der hot aroysgekhapt dem revolver, un der

00:05:50.310 --> 00:05:52.920
un der hot gedronzhet. der hot im dersh- -harget, dershosn.

00:05:53.020 --> 00:05:56.777
dertseylt mir der mayster ⟨MEIER⟩, un zogt er "zolstu visn," zogt er "yetst

00:05:57.340 --> 00:05:58.329
halts enk

00:05:58.875 --> 00:06:01.417
⟨WAS⟩ du krigst" UNK der ⟨MEIER⟩

00:06:01.423 --> 00:06:04.370
"halts enk, vayl s'iz" zogt er "yetst iz nisht lang shoyn di krig."

00:06:05.254 --> 00:06:06.850
ver hot gevolt visn derfun?

00:06:06.710 --> 00:06:09.040
dos iz shoyn geven shpet zumer fir un fertsik?

00:06:06.850 --> 00:06:07.994
zenen zey geblibn

00:06:08.794 --> 00:06:09.544
vos?

00:06:09.544 --> 00:06:11.190
dos iz shoyn geven zumer fir un fertsik?

00:06:11.008 --> 00:06:12.234
fir un fertsik.

00:06:12.804 --> 00:06:13.604
ende z-

00:06:12.860 --> 00:06:15.289
s'iz gevezn ende, bald UNK

00:06:14.640 --> 00:06:16.082
AUGUST fir un fertsik

00:06:15.548 --> 00:06:17.055
UNK ⟨AUGUST⟩ gevezn.

00:06:17.055 --> 00:06:19.727
zogt er tsu mir "halt zikh," un UNK dertseylt.

00:06:20.003 --> 00:06:22.376
yetst, farshteystu, ver hot dos opgemakht

00:06:22.737 --> 00:06:26.224
dem gantsn makhloyke. der man, der WRONEK

00:06:26.331 --> 00:06:27.951
hot gearbet gegn im

00:06:27.951 --> 00:06:29.281
un er hot gezogt az er hot

00:06:29.281 --> 00:06:30.851
mir hobn im bakoyft

00:06:31.090 --> 00:06:33.213
farshteyst? az mir hobn im bakoyft

00:06:33.213 --> 00:06:35.758
un er git oyf mir, mikh gerufn aroyf, y-

00:06:35.832 --> 00:06:37.822
un tsu di GES- tsu GESTAPO

00:06:37.822 --> 00:06:39.222
un gefregt "vos iz?

00:06:39.222 --> 00:06:40.782
fun vanet hostu bakrign a

00:06:40.782 --> 00:06:42.932
a tsol teylung? vos hostu im gegebn?

00:06:42.932 --> 00:06:44.702
vos hostu im, un fun vanet kenstu im?"

00:06:44.702 --> 00:06:48.915
azoy hot im ongehoybn tsu yogn, hob ikh gezogt ikh ken im. er iz geven der direktor bay A.E.G.

00:06:48.915 --> 00:06:50.475
ikh hob ⟨nisht⟩ gehat keyn shum gesheftn

00:06:50.475 --> 00:06:53.121
un ikh hob geboyt dem tramv- ikh hob keyn shum zakhn nisht

00:06:53.159 --> 00:06:54.101
farshteyst?

00:06:54.850 --> 00:06:58.296
dos hot pasirt, farshteystu, demolt. nokh dem hot zikh ongehoybn di gantse

00:06:58.296 --> 00:06:59.416
oyszidlung

00:06:59.416 --> 00:07:00.916
tseganen, tseganen.

00:07:00.916 --> 00:07:01.726
letstn-

00:07:01.726 --> 00:07:04.116
geven d- gloyb ikh dem akht un tsvontsikstn.

00:07:05.076 --> 00:07:06.509
iz gekumen, hot men gef-

00:07:06.509 --> 00:07:09.109
hot men aropgefirt mitn tramvay s- ikh hob do di bilder

00:07:09.210 --> 00:07:11.283
hot men ⟨arop⟩gefirt oykhet

00:07:11.283 --> 00:07:14.976
der, der prezes hot gehat a bruder, hot er geheysn JOZEF RUMKOWSKI.

00:07:15.977 --> 00:07:18.089
JOZEF RUMKOWSKI

00:07:18.089 --> 00:07:19.989
iz geven der direktor fun shpitol.

00:07:20.550 --> 00:07:22.181
er hot gehat a froy.

00:07:22.862 --> 00:07:26.129
hot men ⟨im⟩ oykh geshikt. hot der prezes mitgeforn

00:07:26.305 --> 00:07:28.931
bazaytikn ts- mitn tramvay arayntsugeyn

00:07:29.106 --> 00:07:31.796
iz gekumen tsu, aroptsugeyn oyf ⟨RADA⟩ gas mitn tramvay

00:07:31.796 --> 00:07:34.746
hobn di ale mentshn arayngenumen. m'hot arayngezetst dem bruder.

00:07:35.316 --> 00:07:38.314
der bruder iz shoyn gezitsn, ale mentshn shoyn ⟨arayngan⟩, iz tsugelofn

00:07:39.670 --> 00:07:41.060
d- der BIEBOW

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:42.150
un der FUCHS

00:07:42.150 --> 00:07:45.500
un m'hot ongekhapt dem prezes un dem prezes arayngevorfn in oyto

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:47.060
"UNK farflukhte JUDE

00:07:47.060 --> 00:07:47.831
gey."

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:50.240
iz der prezes avekgeganen.

00:07:50.655 --> 00:07:54.193
shpeter hot men nokh sh- nokh a, shpeter ⟨geven⟩ nokh a transport.

00:07:54.233 --> 00:07:57.298
ikh hob nisht getort forn. ikh hob gedarft tsu blaybn.

00:07:57.304 --> 00:07:58.974
MEINE froy

00:07:58.974 --> 00:08:00.374
mit MEINE kind

00:08:00.374 --> 00:08:01.394
mit MEINE

00:08:01.394 --> 00:08:04.124
shviger un MEINE shve- shvester

00:08:04.124 --> 00:08:06.854
mit di k- mit mayn bruder's kind mit ale

00:08:06.854 --> 00:08:08.340
zey hobn gedarft tsu blaybn.

00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:09.220
un mayne

00:08:09.220 --> 00:08:10.820
shvogers vos zenen do do oykh

00:08:10.820 --> 00:08:12.210
der

00:08:12.210 --> 00:08:14.274
ale tsunezamen

00:08:14.871 --> 00:08:16.814
hot men gedarft tsu blaybn.

00:08:16.814 --> 00:08:18.634
ikh hob nisht getort forn

00:08:18.634 --> 00:08:20.845
hot men gezogt az zey geyen

00:08:20.845 --> 00:08:21.835
⟨vil⟩ ikh oykh geyn.

00:08:21.835 --> 00:08:24.165
ven me khapt mikh, hot men g- git mir a koyl.

00:08:24.165 --> 00:08:26.022
ALSO kurts tsu di zakh

00:08:26.022 --> 00:08:28.162
⟨ikh hob⟩ aropgefirt zey mitn tramvay

00:08:28.162 --> 00:08:30.892
vos zenen geve- der l- letster. keyn shum transport iz nisht geven mer.

00:08:30.892 --> 00:08:32.567
dos iz di letste grupe gevezn

00:08:32.573 --> 00:08:34.052
bin ikh arayngeshprungen

00:08:34.227 --> 00:08:35.233
in vogn

00:08:35.610 --> 00:08:37.600
un ⟨ikh bin⟩ geganen.

00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:39.120
nor a ts- a

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.280
a vokh UNK tsi foroys

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:44.920
hot men gekumen di v- vagonen zenen geganen mitn tramvay, hot men geshikt vagonen

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:47.830
hot men gemuzt aroysnemen, hot men UNK gegebn

00:08:47.830 --> 00:08:49.540
kanen fun milekh

00:08:49.540 --> 00:08:52.505
hot men mitgegebn, zey hobn UNK mentshn zoln erleydikn

00:08:52.505 --> 00:08:55.065
hot men genumen. hot men ge- mitgebrengt tsurik di kanen

00:08:55.065 --> 00:08:57.664
un mir hobn genumen di kanen oyfn, oyfn ⟨barg⟩ aroys

00:08:57.664 --> 00:08:58.934
farshteyst, arop

00:08:58.934 --> 00:09:02.114
hob ikh oyfgedekt a, a kanen, iz gelign a briv.

00:09:02.114 --> 00:09:03.599
inem briv iz geshribn

00:09:04.062 --> 00:09:06.891
"for- geyts nisht, zolts visn ets geyt oyfn toyt."

00:09:07.892 --> 00:09:08.758
geshribn dos.

00:09:08.758 --> 00:09:10.398
hob ikh genumen dem briv

00:09:10.398 --> 00:09:13.088
un arunter⟨UNK⟩, geven JAKUBOWICZ hot er geheysn

00:09:13.088 --> 00:09:14.548
der vitse prezes.

00:09:14.608 --> 00:09:16.815
zayn bruder iz geven RESORT

00:09:16.815 --> 00:09:17.786
un d- k-

00:09:17.786 --> 00:09:19.648
⟨sklad⟩ RESORT bay

00:09:19.654 --> 00:09:23.546
kr- vi hot er geheysn, der bruder mit dem, d-

00:09:24.784 --> 00:09:25.976
kh'vel dir bald zogn

00:09:26.168 --> 00:09:30.468
UNK tsvey ⟨shutfim⟩, zenen geven tsvey UNK, un er iz krank gevorn vi ikh hob im gegebn der

00:09:30.468 --> 00:09:33.168
hot er tsunezamengerufn, der JAKUBOWICZ

00:09:33.168 --> 00:09:36.484
EIN grupe, iz geven WARSZAWKI, s'iz geven UNK

00:09:36.484 --> 00:09:40.978
s'iz gevezn nokh a por, den, iz oykh mitgevezn, ikh hob dir gezogt iz geven tsvey

00:09:40.978 --> 00:09:42.678
brider vos zenen geven slikheners

00:09:42.678 --> 00:09:43.879
BRACIA⟨KOHN⟩

00:09:43.879 --> 00:09:45.589
n- geven in Varshever geto.

00:09:45.589 --> 00:09:46.989
er iz oykh mitgevezn.

00:09:46.989 --> 00:09:50.416
un ikh bin ⟨oyvn⟩ geven. ikh hob zey gegebn dem briv.

00:09:50.416 --> 00:09:51.676
hot men bashlosn

00:09:52.358 --> 00:09:55.139
fun on- dos letste vos iz nisht gevezn kimat di letste

00:09:55.139 --> 00:09:56.401
az me zol nisht geyn.

00:09:58.416 --> 00:10:00.362
dem tsveytn tog in di fri

00:10:00.362 --> 00:10:01.712
ruft er mikh

00:10:01.712 --> 00:10:04.272
⟨BIEBOW⟩ UNK a bafel, ikh zol kumen oyfn BALUTER plats.

00:10:04.272 --> 00:10:08.382
ikh kum arop oyfn BALUTER plats, iz arestirt, UNK arestirt im

00:10:08.382 --> 00:10:09.672
dem

00:10:09.672 --> 00:10:12.740
⟨KOHNen⟩

00:10:12.740 --> 00:10:16.060
genumen im. ikh bin aruntergevorn bal- oyfn gutn ort

00:10:16.060 --> 00:10:17.091
un m'hot im dershosn.

00:10:17.299 --> 00:10:18.963
er hot oysgegebn

00:10:19.037 --> 00:10:19.970
di khevre.

00:10:19.970 --> 00:10:22.322
hot men f- tselozt zey, m'hot nisht gornisht getun.

00:10:23.003 --> 00:10:25.885
dernokh dem bin ikh der letster gevezn fun di letste grupe.

00:10:25.885 --> 00:10:27.421
in di letste grupe

00:10:27.421 --> 00:10:29.555
hot zikh- geven di tsvey slikheners

00:10:29.555 --> 00:10:32.227
der ⟨WEILAND⟩ un der ⟨ACKENBERG⟩

00:10:32.503 --> 00:10:36.128
zenen mitgekumen mit undz. zey hobn ongetun zikh hitlen fun tramvay

00:10:36.128 --> 00:10:37.644
un mitgeforn mit di hitlekh.

00:10:38.325 --> 00:10:39.039
yetst k-

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:39.940
fort men.

00:10:40.570 --> 00:10:43.702
m'iz gekumen keyn AUSCHWITZ, mit di f- di rampe

00:10:43.708 --> 00:10:44.928
hot men geshrign

00:10:44.928 --> 00:10:49.408
"testeylts enk, gets op di kinder, di froyen bazunder, di eltern, gets op di shvigers.

00:10:49.408 --> 00:10:51.138
mayn shviger hot genumen

00:10:51.138 --> 00:10:53.928
mayn yingele, mayn shvoger's yingele

00:10:53.928 --> 00:10:55.088
un d- un

00:10:55.088 --> 00:10:58.098
un, un mayn shveste- un mayn bruder's kind

00:10:58.098 --> 00:10:59.648
dem, ⟨di⟩ shviger mayne

00:10:59.648 --> 00:11:02.281
UND di d- andere shviger, d- der

00:11:02.845 --> 00:11:04.138
vos zi iz do do

00:11:04.296 --> 00:11:08.836
er hot genumen, farshteystu hobn zey g- zayn muter genumen, zayn tatn genumen.

00:11:08.836 --> 00:11:13.286
azoy hot men undz gezogt "rekhts un links." dort, ikh hob dokh nisht gevust ver iz der Mengele

00:11:13.286 --> 00:11:17.219
un di undzere yidn, vos zenen geganen in di pashakes un gearbet, heyst es CANADA

00:11:17.219 --> 00:11:18.369
hot men zey gerufn

00:11:18.369 --> 00:11:19.286
hobn geshrign

00:11:19.286 --> 00:11:22.737
"varfts avek ales, gets op alts, ets geyt UNK in oyvn arayn."

00:11:22.737 --> 00:11:24.641
zey hobn shoyn g- gegebn undz tsu visn.

00:11:24.732 --> 00:11:26.295
kurts tsu di zakh

00:11:26.689 --> 00:11:29.949
bin adurkh, hot men getseylt rekhts un links. ikh bin geganen

00:11:29.949 --> 00:11:31.169
oyf links.

00:11:31.169 --> 00:11:33.879
rekhts l- a bayshpil, ikh gedenk nisht tsu s'iz geven rekhts oder links

00:11:33.879 --> 00:11:37.271
eyn zayt iz geganen tsum toyt. ale mit di kinder zenen gan in di zayt mit di froyen

00:11:37.271 --> 00:11:40.841
MEINE froy iz gegan in di zayt. di ⟨froyen⟩ oykh gegan in di zayt, un di mame

00:11:40.841 --> 00:11:43.500
di mame mit di kinder iz geganen avek tsum oyvn.

00:11:43.500 --> 00:11:44.941
m'iz gekumen tsu geyn shoyn

00:11:45.302 --> 00:11:48.170
hot undz der Mengele hot undz ⟨selektirt⟩.

00:11:48.170 --> 00:11:49.972
yetst kumt men tsu geyn nokh a molt

00:11:49.972 --> 00:11:51.442
nokh a molt a selektsye

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:56.020
m- eyder me geyt arayn in di ka- heyst dos in di, in di

00:11:56.020 --> 00:11:58.950
STUBE v- heyst ⟨zi⟩ WASCHSTUBE hot zi geheysn.

00:11:58.950 --> 00:12:02.184
me krigt dort, hot men gekrign a shtik zeyf, "reyn JUDEN"

00:12:02.184 --> 00:12:04.114
UNK heyst dos do.

00:12:04.114 --> 00:12:05.545
ikh hob dem, ikh ho-

00:12:05.545 --> 00:12:08.025
ikh hob do EIN zakh vos ⟨hot er⟩ keyner nisht gevizn.

00:12:08.025 --> 00:12:09.434
kh'veys nisht tsi ikh hob es mitgenumen.

00:12:09.434 --> 00:12:12.534
d- di yidn, m- me makht fun, m'hot gemakht zeyf. ikh hob dos do.

00:12:12.534 --> 00:12:14.553
dos hobn di rusn ge- UNK. ikh hob di

00:12:14.553 --> 00:12:16.933
dem original. dos hob ikh oykhet.

00:12:17.736 --> 00:12:19.198
nu, ahin, aher

00:12:19.238 --> 00:12:20.601
me geyt tsu shoyn

00:12:20.601 --> 00:12:23.551
arayn. kh'hob mir gekrign a shtik zeyf, un az ikh UNK naket

00:12:24.925 --> 00:12:27.450
me heyst mikh geyn oyf di tsveyte zayt.

00:12:28.401 --> 00:12:34.759
hot zikh gegat, ikh hob gegat di da- yekes bay mir vos zey hobn gearbet bay mir. git der yeke eyner a ⟨shrey⟩, geven SCHNEIDER heyst er

00:12:34.759 --> 00:12:38.351
"DASS IST DER OBERMEISTER VON DIE ELEKTRISCHE STRASSENBAHN"

00:12:38.712 --> 00:12:39.569
ALSO

00:12:39.569 --> 00:12:41.948
"WIR BRAUCHEN" zogt er "STRASSENBAHN ARBEITER"

00:12:41.948 --> 00:12:44.662
azoy hot er mikh avekgenumen tsurik oyf di d-

00:12:44.685 --> 00:12:45.855
azoy bin ikh geganen

00:12:45.855 --> 00:12:47.645
hot men mikh tsugeteylt in a blok

00:12:47.645 --> 00:12:49.075
hot men di froy avekgenumen

00:12:49.075 --> 00:12:50.195
un di kinder m-

00:12:50.195 --> 00:12:53.225
zenen nebekh gegan ikh veys nisht. di froyen zenen geganen bazunder

00:12:53.225 --> 00:12:55.596
ALSO m'hot undz tsugefirt in a blok

00:12:55.596 --> 00:12:57.096
in AUSCHWITZ, in BIRKENAU

00:12:57.096 --> 00:12:58.716
dos heyst blok akhtsn.

00:12:58.716 --> 00:13:00.154
bin ikh arayngefaln

00:13:00.970 --> 00:13:02.162
tsu a blok

00:13:03.028 --> 00:13:04.999
merders, banditn

00:13:04.999 --> 00:13:06.077
gazlonim

00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:07.210
zenen gevezn

00:13:07.210 --> 00:13:09.620
der OBERKAPO hot geheysn WALTER

00:13:09.620 --> 00:13:12.890
der iz gevezn, farshteystu, er hot geharget zayn eygene froy

00:13:12.890 --> 00:13:14.900
iz gan- a hoykher

00:13:14.900 --> 00:13:16.480
gantsn ⟨a⟩ tatuirt

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:17.116
do

00:13:17.116 --> 00:13:18.192
a froy.

00:13:18.503 --> 00:13:20.263
der tsveyter iz geven EMIL

00:13:20.263 --> 00:13:22.530
der driter iz geven h- der tsigayner.

00:13:22.738 --> 00:13:25.027
der ferder iz gevezn a yid, DAWID.

00:13:25.270 --> 00:13:28.892
der fer- fifter iz gevezn an ungerer. er hot geheysn DIMANT.

00:13:29.573 --> 00:13:31.609
dort s'iz gevezn UNK vi ⟨di⟩ CANADA

00:13:33.015 --> 00:13:36.772
un ikh bin arayngefirt in a blok, iz geven hundert akhtsn.

00:13:36.981 --> 00:13:38.927
in dem blok, m'iz arayngekumen

00:13:38.927 --> 00:13:41.357
iz gevezn, der royter hot men im gerufn

00:13:41.554 --> 00:13:42.729
tsvey

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.564
zenen brider gevezn, tsvey brider.

00:13:46.043 --> 00:13:49.834
eyner hot im gerufn dem Parizer, oder a tsveyter hot gezogt der Varshever.

00:13:50.278 --> 00:13:53.886
m'iz arayngekumen dort tsu geyn. es iz gevezn di oyvn in der mit

00:13:53.886 --> 00:13:56.246
⟨dort⟩ es iz nisht geven keyn pritshn, nor s'iz geven a

00:13:56.246 --> 00:13:57.676
a pritsh azoy aroyf

00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:00.036
UNK fun breter

00:14:00.036 --> 00:14:04.016
un fun di zayt, un ⟨m'iz⟩ azoy ey- gelign eyner oyfn tsveytn hot gehaltn oyf di akslen, azoy.

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:06.095
kurts tsu di zakh, hot er geshrign

00:14:06.095 --> 00:14:08.584
"ver iz geven a politsyant? gets aher di politsyantn

00:14:08.584 --> 00:14:10.054
gets aher dem un dem.

00:14:10.054 --> 00:14:11.674
gets aher di slikheners."

00:14:12.132 --> 00:14:13.712
keyner hot zikh nisht tsugeshtelt.

00:14:13.802 --> 00:14:15.314
hot er geshrign "gets aher

00:14:15.314 --> 00:14:16.174
⟨WEILAND⟩."

00:14:16.174 --> 00:14:18.634
der ⟨WEILAND⟩ hot zikh ongetun a hitl

00:14:18.634 --> 00:14:20.996
fun di p- UNK un di A.K.B.

00:14:20.996 --> 00:14:23.876
nor er hot gehat a bruder vos er iz gevezn in UNK lager

00:14:23.876 --> 00:14:25.516
a fayner yung.

00:14:25.516 --> 00:14:27.245
m'hot geshrign, geshrign

00:14:27.285 --> 00:14:31.340
un keyner. hot er gezogt "ikh bin der ⟨WEILAND⟩." er hot geheysn ⟨WEILAND⟩. s'iz ⟨geven⟩ zayn bruder

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:35.340
hot er ongehoybn im tsu shlogn, di tsvey khevre, di tsvey brider.

00:14:35.340 --> 00:14:37.132
s'iz geven geferlekh.

00:14:37.132 --> 00:14:41.152
mit eyn molt hot im, ikh hob gehat a grupe, dos hot geheysn, ikh hob UNK di foto

00:14:41.152 --> 00:14:42.972
⟨PAPERMANS⟩. katsovim gevezn.

00:14:42.972 --> 00:14:44.737
geven shtarke yungen, farshteyst?

00:14:44.737 --> 00:14:47.107
⟨hobn⟩ zey geheysn di, heyst di ayzerne gvardye bay mir.

00:14:47.107 --> 00:14:50.067
zey hobn gekopet un ⟨geholfn⟩ t- tsien di shines

00:14:50.067 --> 00:14:54.208
der PAPERMAN UNK hot nisht gekent oyshaltn ⟨nor er hot gevust⟩ UNK ⟨iz er⟩ tsu tsu dem

00:14:54.208 --> 00:14:55.118
a hoykher yung

00:14:55.118 --> 00:14:56.948
un m'hot im gegebn dem

00:14:56.948 --> 00:14:58.242
⟨shtubn dinst⟩

00:14:58.242 --> 00:15:00.792
u, iz dort gevaksn a UNK

00:15:01.457 --> 00:15:03.408
iz der tsveyter aroysgelofn

00:15:03.583 --> 00:15:04.572
brengen

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:08.980
UNK hot gezen ⟨dos iz geven tsu⟩ fir man azane katsovim

00:15:08.980 --> 00:15:09.690
KLEIN

00:15:09.690 --> 00:15:11.660
PAPERMAN, BENKEL, UNK

00:15:11.660 --> 00:15:13.787
di fir katsovim vos zenen gevezn di

00:15:13.793 --> 00:15:16.270
hoypt ayzerne yungen vos zey hobn gearbet baym tramvay

00:15:16.270 --> 00:15:18.961
zenen zey aroysgelofn UNK un hot gebrengt

00:15:18.961 --> 00:15:20.061
ver iz gekumen?

00:15:20.061 --> 00:15:21.279
Moyshe Khosid.

00:15:22.230 --> 00:15:23.878
Moyshe Khosid hot gegat

00:15:24.137 --> 00:15:25.636
kurves in di geto

00:15:25.636 --> 00:15:27.304
un der prezes hot im avekgeshikt.

00:15:27.985 --> 00:15:29.256
vos hot pasirt?

00:15:29.256 --> 00:15:31.404
Moyshe Khosid iz gekumen tsu geyn

00:15:32.355 --> 00:15:33.986
zogt er "vemen hostu geshlogn?"

00:15:34.735 --> 00:15:38.053
Moyshe, Moyshe Khosid, ven der prezes iz gekumen, hot er im geharget.

00:15:38.818 --> 00:15:40.840
un UNK "vemen hostu geshlogn?

00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:43.852
vos hostu gemakht?" un er hot im gegebn nokh a ZBEK tsu

00:15:43.852 --> 00:15:45.394
"dos iz mayne khaveyrim"

00:15:46.058 --> 00:15:51.755
farshteyst? azoy hot men UNK, un ikh bin geblibn dort in dem lager, un dort iz gevezn

00:15:51.863 --> 00:15:52.633
UNK.

00:15:53.213 --> 00:15:57.463
UND der mentsh dort iz geven, ot der DIMANT iz gevezn an ungerisher yid.

00:15:57.463 --> 00:15:59.433
⟨yeder⟩ tog hot men gekhapt

00:15:59.433 --> 00:16:00.613
tsen man

00:16:00.613 --> 00:16:02.974
vos zenen UNK aroysgeganen oysern lager

00:16:02.974 --> 00:16:06.754
un tsurikgekumen IST nor, hot er gehat hundert man, iz tsurikgekumen nayntsik man.

00:16:06.754 --> 00:16:08.914
hot er gehat akhtsik man, iz tsurikgekumen zibetsik man.

00:16:08.914 --> 00:16:09.854
⟨yeder⟩ tog.

00:16:09.854 --> 00:16:12.314
mit eyn molt hot er mikh gekhapt oykh mit

00:16:12.314 --> 00:16:13.614
di grupe

00:16:13.918 --> 00:16:16.128
khapt mikh UNK mit in di grupe

00:16:16.128 --> 00:16:18.288
zogt er UNK er vet gornisht tun.

00:16:18.846 --> 00:16:20.139
"ikh hob yortsayt."

00:16:21.107 --> 00:16:21.928
"ha?"

00:16:22.035 --> 00:16:25.025
"yortsayt, yo?" hot er undz arayngenumen, UNK ⟨oykh⟩ nisht gevust vos ⟨zol men⟩ tun

00:16:25.025 --> 00:16:27.005
arayngerufn in barak arayn

00:16:27.005 --> 00:16:33.234
un hot zikh anidergesh- un mir zikh anidergeshtelt sh- ale, un er hot ge UNK -GADAL VEYISKADASH SHMEY RABO UNK

00:16:33.234 --> 00:16:34.484
UNK geheysn

00:16:34.484 --> 00:16:35.994
farshteyt, gezogt kadesh

00:16:35.994 --> 00:16:37.954
un mir hobn gezogt UNK omeyn

00:16:37.954 --> 00:16:40.878
un m'hot undz gegebn a ⟨paltike⟩ broyt, un er hot es nokhgelozt.

00:16:42.285 --> 00:16:45.671
un ikh, hot men genumen tsum, tsu boyen di shines

00:16:45.829 --> 00:16:47.409
tsu boyen di shines

00:16:47.618 --> 00:16:50.466
oyser, fun AUSCHWITZ aroys in vald arayn.

00:16:50.466 --> 00:16:51.897
dort hobn zey geboyt

00:16:52.174 --> 00:16:53.973
a groysn krematoryum.

00:16:54.705 --> 00:16:56.855
nisht gevorn fertik, farshteyt zikh, brenen

00:16:56.855 --> 00:16:59.295
zeyer a groysn. m'hot ⟨zikh⟩ gebrent UNK m'hot dokh gebrent

00:16:59.295 --> 00:17:01.575
in di rivn oykhet aruntergevorfn

00:17:01.575 --> 00:17:04.075
un dort hot men geboyt ⟨ayn⟩ a rizn

00:17:04.075 --> 00:17:05.951
hob ikh gemakht di shines.

00:17:05.951 --> 00:17:07.551
in dem blok

00:17:07.551 --> 00:17:09.471
iz gevezn nor UNK

00:17:09.471 --> 00:17:11.231
un iz geven a lome kapo

00:17:11.231 --> 00:17:12.218
bay tog

00:17:12.218 --> 00:17:13.708
iz er geven a soyne yisroel.

00:17:13.708 --> 00:17:15.548
un bay di nakht hot er dertseylt

00:17:15.548 --> 00:17:16.708
vi di rusn geyen

00:17:16.708 --> 00:17:18.521
vu zey geyen un ven me geyt

00:17:18.521 --> 00:17:21.581
do iz do yidn vos ikh hob do getrofn, zenen gevezn dort.

00:17:21.581 --> 00:17:23.571
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu

00:17:23.643 --> 00:17:25.007
mit eyn molt

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:33.056
iz do a yid vos er iz geven a ⟨PUPILEK⟩. veyst UNK ⟨PUPIL⟩? host gehert shoyn? bist, d'host nisht gegat mit mentshn tsu tun vegn AUSCHWITZ?

00:17:32.780 --> 00:17:34.380
yo, ober ⟨PUPIL⟩, vos iz?

00:17:34.058 --> 00:17:35.925
nisht gehert a pipl? a pipl?

00:17:35.730 --> 00:17:36.470
vos iz dos?

00:17:36.235 --> 00:17:37.570
host nisht gehert ⟨vegn⟩ keyn pipl?

00:17:37.464 --> 00:17:38.644
nu, lomir hern.

00:17:37.845 --> 00:17:40.735
a pipl iz gevezn UNK vos zey hobn nisht gehat keyn froyen

00:17:41.297 --> 00:17:43.096
hot er oysgenitst dos yingele.

00:17:42.714 --> 00:17:43.524
ah

00:17:43.879 --> 00:17:46.556
hot oysgenitst dos yingl. ⟨iz er⟩ geven a pipl

00:17:47.153 --> 00:17:51.619
un der hot gegat a khaver vos er hot gevust ales f- fun dem kapo, un m'hot ⟨geshoybn⟩.

00:17:52.789 --> 00:17:53.866
vos hot pasirt?

00:17:53.866 --> 00:17:55.334
pasirt, farshteystu

00:17:55.334 --> 00:17:57.299
der iz antlofn

00:17:57.299 --> 00:18:00.329
i- ts- hob ikh gegat, ikh hob geboyt dem tramvay

00:18:00.329 --> 00:18:03.999
iz er tsugekumen ts- d- dortn, es iz nisht di tramvay, di shines, arayn in vald arayn

00:18:03.999 --> 00:18:06.069
⟨hot er⟩ gehat a drezne. veyst vos a drezne iz?

00:18:06.069 --> 00:18:09.432
vos fort oyf a, azoy vi a rover, oyf di shines

00:18:09.432 --> 00:18:12.342
un dos fort zikh a- dos loyft UNK, azoy shnel geyt er

00:18:12.342 --> 00:18:14.594
iz UNK gekumen tsu UNK "⟨lomikh⟩ dos do"

00:18:14.594 --> 00:18:15.984
un ikh hob es gegebn.

00:18:16.141 --> 00:18:17.179
ikh hob dokh moyre gehat

00:18:17.179 --> 00:18:18.061
a yid

00:18:18.456 --> 00:18:21.756
hot er zikh gegebn, un iz avekgeforn mit ⟨di⟩ dos, un er iz antlofn.

00:18:21.756 --> 00:18:23.996
nu, hobn zey gezogt ⟨hot men im⟩ geharget

00:18:24.784 --> 00:18:26.806
UNK gelebt

00:18:26.806 --> 00:18:28.540
azoy iz gevezn ⟨yede⟩ tog.

00:18:28.540 --> 00:18:30.970
⟨yede⟩ tog UNK pasirt vos andersh.

00:18:30.970 --> 00:18:33.756
kurts tsu di zakh, ikh hob gearbet bay di shines, farshteystu.

00:18:33.756 --> 00:18:34.916
mit eyn molt

00:18:35.044 --> 00:18:36.860
mit eyn molt, farshteystu

00:18:37.356 --> 00:18:39.290
zogt mir, farshteystu

00:18:39.955 --> 00:18:41.990
"gey arayn in lager arayn."

00:18:41.990 --> 00:18:46.932
UNK m'hot gekumen tsu geyn tsurik fun di arbet. ikh bin UNK gekumen tsu geyn shtendik a bisele shpeter, farshteyst?

00:18:46.932 --> 00:18:49.746
ikh bin UNK nokh dem ⟨hot men mikh⟩ tsugeteylt tsu di FLAK komando

00:18:49.746 --> 00:18:51.196
veyst vos FLAK komando iz?

00:18:52.189 --> 00:18:53.915
az me bombet.

00:18:52.408 --> 00:18:54.106
mh

00:18:53.915 --> 00:18:59.593
iz a bombe vos falt arunter, hob ikh gemuzt geyn, ⟨an elektrik⟩ oys⟨UNK⟩. rizikirt dos lebn.

00:18:59.593 --> 00:19:01.537
hob ikh UNK tsugeteylt, bin ikh geblibn

00:19:01.537 --> 00:19:03.117
bay di FLAK komande

00:19:03.117 --> 00:19:04.364
bay hundert

00:19:04.364 --> 00:19:06.914
hundert geve- in di lagern gevezn

00:19:06.914 --> 00:19:08.804
in tsvey shtubn akhtsn

00:19:08.804 --> 00:19:10.769
un tsvontsik iz gevezn di

00:19:10.769 --> 00:19:12.779
di khevre, nor di kapos

00:19:12.779 --> 00:19:14.189
tsugeteylt hot men gemakht

00:19:14.189 --> 00:19:15.529
a FLAK komando

00:19:15.529 --> 00:19:18.107
bin ikh tsugeteylt gevorn tsu di FLAK komando

00:19:18.107 --> 00:19:19.237
ot dort iz UNK

00:19:19.237 --> 00:19:21.737
kurts tsu di zakh, vos hot, vos hot pasirt?

00:19:21.737 --> 00:19:23.957
pasirt hot, farshteystu, az di khevre

00:19:23.957 --> 00:19:26.787
hobn geshoybn. veyst ⟨vos taytsh⟩ geshoybn?

00:19:26.787 --> 00:19:28.426
host gekrign a gut hemd

00:19:28.426 --> 00:19:31.116
hot er, der kapo, tsugenumen, hot er gegebn a brudik hemd

00:19:31.116 --> 00:19:34.404
un zey hobn es farkoyft aroys tsu di poyerim un gebrengt esn.

00:19:35.187 --> 00:19:40.757
un ikh bin geven aroys- d- oyser di geto, un ikh bin aroysgeganen mit, me zukht, di bom- di bom- me darf zukhn di bombes

00:19:40.757 --> 00:19:42.397
hobn zey geshoybn

00:19:42.397 --> 00:19:44.097
un m'hot zey derkhapt.

00:19:44.569 --> 00:19:46.931
m'hot geganen in di lager avekshikn

00:19:46.931 --> 00:19:48.451
a shtraf komando

00:19:48.451 --> 00:19:51.331
iz geven ikh un a yid vos er hot geheysn

00:19:52.939 --> 00:19:53.979
vi heyst er?

00:19:55.065 --> 00:19:57.084
hot beyde kinder do do in UNK

00:20:00.702 --> 00:20:02.150
kh'vel dir bald zogn vi er heyst.

00:20:04.110 --> 00:20:08.199
ALSO ikh mit nokh a yid, kh- kh'vel dos kumen bald oyf dem nomen

00:20:08.199 --> 00:20:12.131
un m'hot geganen mit, farshteystu, m'hot undz avekgeshikt in a lager arayn

00:20:12.131 --> 00:20:15.801
shtraf komande, hundert un tsvey perzonen zenen gevezn

00:20:15.801 --> 00:20:17.267
nor kapos

00:20:17.863 --> 00:20:20.776
un undz ze'mir geven di tsvey yidn, ikh un

00:20:21.357 --> 00:20:22.802
Feder, Leybl Feder.

00:20:23.989 --> 00:20:27.939
ikh un Leybl Feder zenen mir gevezn di tsvey oyf⟨UNK⟩ vos ⟨iz⟩ mitgeganen mit di grupe

00:20:27.939 --> 00:20:31.619
m'iz gekumen arayn. dem ALTENHAMMER, ALTEHAMMER iz geven a lager

00:20:31.619 --> 00:20:32.979
vu s'iz gevezn

00:20:32.979 --> 00:20:35.070
italyener

00:20:35.070 --> 00:20:38.840
un d- di UNK hobn zey demolst shoyn aroysgelozt, m'iz fray, s'iz shoyn gevorn a bisl beser

00:20:38.840 --> 00:20:43.225
un mir zenen arayn, dort hot men ge- dos iz geven d- oyf poylish hot dos geheysn

00:20:43.225 --> 00:20:45.465
STARA KUZNIA.

00:20:45.465 --> 00:20:48.299
dort iz geven a g- a grub, a d- koyln grub.

00:20:48.299 --> 00:20:51.669
hot men geboyt dort ⟨in⟩ oyvn, a KOMIN

00:20:51.669 --> 00:20:55.320
spetsyal, hot men undz dort gebrengt. m'iz gekumen dort ahin

00:20:55.697 --> 00:20:56.923
iz gevezn

00:20:57.908 --> 00:20:59.356
zekhtsik protsent

00:20:59.356 --> 00:21:00.906
vos zenen gevezn UNK

00:21:00.906 --> 00:21:02.256
f- fun Lodzh

00:21:02.256 --> 00:21:06.336
nor eyder ikh UNK dertseyln, oyf di kurts dertseyln, hob ikh fargesn in gantsn, dos iz dos vikhtikste

00:21:06.336 --> 00:21:09.871
ALSO bin ikh gevezn dort in lager, ikh bin, eyder ikh bin geganen dort arayn

00:21:09.871 --> 00:21:12.181
bin aheymgekumen fun dem a- fun dem tramvay

00:21:12.181 --> 00:21:13.491
⟨vos⟩ ikh hob geleygt di shines

00:21:13.491 --> 00:21:15.274
vos hot pasirt?

00:21:15.390 --> 00:21:17.544
loyft adurkh a kleyn yingele

00:21:18.073 --> 00:21:20.530
khapt im der kapo DIMANT

00:21:20.807 --> 00:21:23.403
khapt dos kindl, un dos yingl heybt on tsu shrayen

00:21:23.403 --> 00:21:24.873
zogt er "ikh vel dir gornisht tun.

00:21:24.873 --> 00:21:27.913
ikh hob" zogt er "mayns a yingele in froyen lager mit."

00:21:28.063 --> 00:21:30.402
s'iz do tsvey yingelekh in gantsn in dem lager.

00:21:30.510 --> 00:21:32.601
hot er im gekhapt, ⟨UNK⟩ mir undz in blok

00:21:32.601 --> 00:21:37.981
zogt er "ikh vel dir gornisht tun. na" zogt er "a shtikl broyt." zogt er "vos tustu?" zogt er "na, ikh vel zikh UNK teyln" zogt er "mit mayn tatn."

00:21:38.050 --> 00:21:40.055
"ver bist? vi heyst der tate?"

00:21:40.298 --> 00:21:42.134
"mayn tate heyst ⟨PYKORZ⟩

00:21:42.134 --> 00:21:43.616
⟨bay mir⟩ KOPELMAN"

00:21:43.960 --> 00:21:44.969
mayn bruder.

00:21:44.969 --> 00:21:47.329
der tsveyter bruder fun PIOTRKOW TRYBUNALSKI

00:21:47.655 --> 00:21:49.854
ikh hob dos gehert un hot im gegebn a shtikl broyt

00:21:49.854 --> 00:21:54.704
"UNK dir nokh a broyt," zogt er "ikh hob gornisht getun." hot er nokhgelo- "vu iz d- vu, vu iz der tate? in velekhn blok?"

00:21:54.704 --> 00:21:56.184
zogt er "tsvey un tsvontsik."

00:21:57.190 --> 00:21:59.726
tsvey un tsvontsik. vos hob ikh getun?

00:21:59.726 --> 00:22:06.046
m'hot tsugemakht dem lager, un m'hot UNK dos yingele antlofn, bin ikh nokhgelofn dem yingele. ikh bin arayngekumen, hob ikh getrofn mayn bruder

00:22:06.046 --> 00:22:07.168
mit dem yingele.

00:22:07.168 --> 00:22:10.787
dos yingele, vos hobn zey getun? ⟨yede⟩ tog zenen zey aroysgeganen fun

00:22:10.787 --> 00:22:14.017
lager un, un ganen arayn in froyen lager.

00:22:14.017 --> 00:22:17.248
dertseylt mir mayn bruder, er hot getrofn mayn froy.

00:22:18.132 --> 00:22:20.269
zog ikh "veystu vos? ikh volt zi gevolt zen."

00:22:20.393 --> 00:22:21.790
zogt er "veystu vos?

00:22:21.790 --> 00:22:23.297
UNK ⟨vilst⟩ rizikirn

00:22:23.297 --> 00:22:27.427
vestu mitgeyn mit di" UNK, hobn gefirt UNK di tsvey yingelekh hobn gefirt dem dishl

00:22:27.427 --> 00:22:29.912
un tsvey zenen mitgeganen un geshtupt dem vogn

00:22:29.912 --> 00:22:31.482
zogt er "KOMM mit."

00:22:31.482 --> 00:22:33.992
hob ikh mikh aroysge- aroysge⟨UNK⟩ ⟨azoy a⟩ rizike

00:22:33.992 --> 00:22:36.139
aroysgan UNK in di fri fun lager

00:22:36.139 --> 00:22:39.259
un nokhgelofn mit mayn bruder un geshtanen untn bay dem dishl.

00:22:39.259 --> 00:22:41.750
me kumt tsu tsu di vakhe, zogt der vakhe "vos tuts ets do?

00:22:41.750 --> 00:22:42.800
bistu nor tsvey."

00:22:42.800 --> 00:22:47.103
zogt er "m'hot gekrign, s'iz zeyer shver haynt oystsureynikn dort bay di froyen lager di klozetn"

00:22:47.103 --> 00:22:49.838
zogt er "hot men gekrign nokh eyner." zogt er "gey."

00:22:49.838 --> 00:22:51.838
azoy bin ikh arayngekumen in froyen lager.

00:22:51.838 --> 00:22:53.358
ikh hob gezen mayn froy.

00:22:53.358 --> 00:22:54.593
zog ikh

00:22:54.593 --> 00:22:56.923
"⟨OB⟩ zol zayn" zog ikh "a, a bombe harget mikh

00:22:56.923 --> 00:22:58.553
oder ikh gey tsu di drotn

00:22:58.553 --> 00:23:00.083
ikh vil nisht do zayn mer."

00:23:00.083 --> 00:23:03.148
azoy bin ikh tsurikgeganen in lager arayn. mayn bruder hob ikh gezen

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:06.230
iz gevezn di STRAF komande

00:23:06.230 --> 00:23:08.220
bin ikh geganen avek mit di STRAF komande.

00:23:08.220 --> 00:23:11.410
bin ikh gekumen dort ahin in lager, iz geven fil Lodzher

00:23:11.410 --> 00:23:13.766
shoyn dort gevezn. m'hot UNK

00:23:13.766 --> 00:23:15.446
un dort hobn zey genumen di berg

00:23:15.446 --> 00:23:18.446
hot men gemakht zeyer untn iz shoyn gelign ⟨der⟩ fundament iz shoyn gelign

00:23:18.446 --> 00:23:20.816
un dort iz gevezn yede tog.

00:23:20.816 --> 00:23:22.126
hobn zey geharget

00:23:22.126 --> 00:23:25.136
di zelbe mayse, tsen, tsvelef perzonen. vi azoy geharget?

00:23:25.136 --> 00:23:27.233
di ⟨LORRIES⟩, UNK

00:23:27.233 --> 00:23:29.343
dos iz di vegelekh, vegl on dem

00:23:29.343 --> 00:23:31.663
me leygt zamd. dos UNK

00:23:31.767 --> 00:23:34.099
hobn zey geladevet do di shteyner dort in dos

00:23:34.099 --> 00:23:36.729
un m'hot aruntergelozt, un di mentshn zenen geshtanen oyf di shines

00:23:36.786 --> 00:23:41.420
iz geganen UNK opgehakt dem kop, opgehakt di fis, opgehakt di, azoy iz dort gevezn.

00:23:41.967 --> 00:23:43.527
un dort hob ikh getrofn

00:23:43.527 --> 00:23:45.557
mayne dem ⟨KUPERMANS⟩ vos er iz do do

00:23:45.557 --> 00:23:46.837
im mitn bruder

00:23:46.837 --> 00:23:49.267
un mayn shvoger hob ikh dort getrofn.

00:23:49.267 --> 00:23:51.437
zey zenen shoyn dort gevezn

00:23:51.437 --> 00:23:52.649
in dem lager.

00:23:52.649 --> 00:23:54.689
azoy zenen mir dort gevezn, farshteystu

00:23:54.689 --> 00:23:55.939
un dort ⟨hob ikh⟩ vayter gemakht

00:23:55.939 --> 00:23:57.079
mit di shines

00:23:57.079 --> 00:23:59.606
vayter geleygt shines. dort hobn zey oykh geboyt

00:23:59.606 --> 00:24:02.026
tsu tsum, farshteystu, s'hot geboyt dem shteyn

00:24:02.026 --> 00:24:03.296
hot men dort geboyt

00:24:03.296 --> 00:24:05.026
azoy ⟨iz⟩ bin ikh gekumen

00:24:05.026 --> 00:24:05.689
keyn

00:24:05.689 --> 00:24:07.107
heyst dos d- keyn

00:24:07.107 --> 00:24:09.265
UNK BIRK- keyn ALTHAMMER.

00:24:09.338 --> 00:24:11.804
fun ALTHAMMER gekumen tsu geyn ⟨muzn mir undz⟩ hobn

00:24:11.804 --> 00:24:14.624
heybt zikh ⟨on⟩ a frishe mayse az ⟨me muz⟩ geyn oyf toytn marsh

00:24:14.624 --> 00:24:15.726
zenen mir aroysgeganen.

00:24:15.726 --> 00:24:17.586
mir ale lagern geyen aroys.

00:24:17.586 --> 00:24:19.756
hot men ongehoybn, m'hot undz tsuzamengerufn

00:24:19.756 --> 00:24:21.826
zenen gekumen fun AUSCHWITZ, zenen gekumen

00:24:21.826 --> 00:24:23.765
fun di zayt di umedum lagern

00:24:23.765 --> 00:24:28.215
un ⟨m'iz⟩ adurkhgeganen ts- tsu ALTHAMMER zenen gekumen. mir zenen aroysgeganen dort. m-

00:24:28.215 --> 00:24:29.976
oyfn veg der vos hot nisht gekent geyn

00:24:29.976 --> 00:24:32.906
iz geforn Mengele UNK fun hintn, un m'hot geshosn

00:24:32.906 --> 00:24:35.136
der vos iz geblibn shteyn fun hintn iz geblibn dershosn.

00:24:35.136 --> 00:24:37.847
azoy zenen mir geganen tsu fus tsvey tog.

00:24:37.847 --> 00:24:40.087
oyfn veg iz grupes militer.

00:24:40.087 --> 00:24:41.787
m'iz tsugekumen tsu BRESLAU

00:24:42.582 --> 00:24:43.791
hobn di rusn

00:24:43.797 --> 00:24:47.175
⟨fun⟩ eyn zayt ⟨hot men shoyn⟩ geshosn oyfn veg, hot men shoyn nisht gekent geyn.

00:24:47.175 --> 00:24:50.185
zenen mir geganen ⟨durkh⟩ di felder adurkh, un m'iz arayngekumen ⟨nokh⟩ BRESLAU

00:24:50.185 --> 00:24:51.472
iz dort gevezn

00:24:51.472 --> 00:24:53.512
a tsigelnye, iz geven a froyen lager

00:24:53.512 --> 00:24:55.402
iz gelign UNK

00:24:55.402 --> 00:25:00.246
UNK

00:25:00.246 --> 00:25:01.726
I TAM UNK

00:25:01.726 --> 00:25:03.790
dort zenen mir arayngan in di stodoles.

00:25:03.790 --> 00:25:06.060
m'iz gelign, oyfn veg hobn di daytshn ⟨shoyn ⟩

00:25:06.060 --> 00:25:09.277
⟨geshtanen⟩ gekukt oyf undz di froyen mit kinder

00:25:09.277 --> 00:25:12.517
zenen mir arayn in dem UNK bay nakht arayn. m'iz dort gelign

00:25:12.517 --> 00:25:16.258
farshteystu. ⟨zenen⟩ mir gelign in stodoles, un UNK gelign dort, vu s'iz nor geganen

00:25:16.258 --> 00:25:17.898
arayngepakt.

00:25:17.898 --> 00:25:19.105
in di fri

00:25:19.105 --> 00:25:21.165
iz nishto keyn eyn eyntsiker daytsh.

00:25:21.165 --> 00:25:22.595
alts iz antlofn.

00:25:22.595 --> 00:25:23.801
alts iz nishto.

00:25:24.820 --> 00:25:26.793
heybt men on, mentshn zenen antlofn

00:25:26.793 --> 00:25:29.003
a sakh zenen antlofn aroys in shtot, UNK

00:25:29.003 --> 00:25:30.993
⟨v- ver⟩ zenen geven mid, farfaln

00:25:30.993 --> 00:25:33.744
⟨veln trakhtn⟩ vu ken men geyn? me ken nisht geyn, m'iz gelign

00:25:33.744 --> 00:25:34.634
zenen mir gelign.

00:25:34.634 --> 00:25:36.904
a zeyger tsvey ⟨un⟩ halb dray

00:25:36.904 --> 00:25:38.258
di daytshn ongekumen.

00:25:38.258 --> 00:25:39.798
un dort oyfn feld iz geven

00:25:39.798 --> 00:25:42.298
a zaytiker UNK.

00:25:42.298 --> 00:25:43.780
dort iz geshtanen vagonen

00:25:43.780 --> 00:25:46.860
un fun dort hot men undz gefirt avek.

00:25:46.860 --> 00:25:50.531
fun dort hot men undz avekgefirt, farshteystu, dos heyst MAUTHAUSEN.

00:25:50.723 --> 00:25:52.128
UNK MAUTHAUSEN.

00:25:52.128 --> 00:25:54.368
m'iz gekumen nokh MAUTHAUSEN

00:25:54.368 --> 00:25:56.984
fil gepakt mentshn.

00:25:56.984 --> 00:26:00.794
s'iz nishto UNK ⟨hot men undz⟩ gegebn shoyn a gute zup un UNK oykh a sakh

00:26:00.794 --> 00:26:03.727
fun Lodzh gevezn dort. kh'hob getrofn mayns a kuzin

00:26:04.560 --> 00:26:06.057
fun dem

00:26:06.057 --> 00:26:09.096
un dort mit mir, ikh bin ge- mitge⟨UNK⟩ shoyn gevorn a

00:26:09.096 --> 00:26:10.116
a goen

00:26:10.116 --> 00:26:12.076
vayl ikh bin nokh gekumen mit di kapos.

00:26:10.803 --> 00:26:13.693
dos iz shoyn onfang finef un fertsikstn

00:26:13.613 --> 00:26:14.463
JA, JA.

00:26:13.693 --> 00:26:16.580
haltn mir shoyn, yo? vinter finef un fertsik.

00:26:16.343 --> 00:26:18.442
neyn, s'iz nokh gevezn gleyb ikh ende

00:26:18.516 --> 00:26:19.691
ende JANUARY.

00:26:19.782 --> 00:26:21.278
ende, ende

00:26:21.733 --> 00:26:23.352
yanuar finef un fertsik.

00:26:23.252 --> 00:26:24.520
neyn, anfang

00:26:24.232 --> 00:26:25.552
anfang yanuar?

00:26:24.962 --> 00:26:27.812
JA, s'iz gevezn dakht zikh mir yanuar, oder s'iz geven nokh detsember.

00:26:27.332 --> 00:26:28.572
ende detsember?

00:26:28.352 --> 00:26:29.209
JA.

00:26:29.485 --> 00:26:31.827
⟨m'iz⟩ dort ahingekumen tsu geyn, ⟨hob ikh⟩ dort getrofn

00:26:31.827 --> 00:26:33.140
nor ikh bin nokh gekumen mit di

00:26:33.140 --> 00:26:35.728
mit di, mit di, mit di khevre, mit di banditn

00:26:35.728 --> 00:26:39.244
hundert un tsvey man, hot men undz gehaltn di gantse, zenen mir ganen vayter mit zey.

00:26:40.133 --> 00:26:42.746
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu, hob ikh dort getrofn

00:26:42.746 --> 00:26:44.526
mayn kuzin mitn tatn

00:26:44.526 --> 00:26:45.926
hot nisht gegat tsu esn.

00:26:45.926 --> 00:26:47.326
in lager

00:26:47.326 --> 00:26:48.367
in ALTHAMMER

00:26:48.367 --> 00:26:50.347
iz im geven voyl.

00:26:50.347 --> 00:26:52.217
mir hot men nisht gegebn

00:26:52.217 --> 00:26:52.957
keyn zupe.

00:26:52.957 --> 00:26:55.030
er hot gegat zup, hot gearbet in di ⟨kokh⟩

00:26:55.030 --> 00:26:57.210
aroysgekumen tsu geyn tsu gebn oykhet.

00:26:57.210 --> 00:26:59.090
er hot gegat a brilyantl in

00:26:59.090 --> 00:27:01.067
in dos do, hot es gegebn

00:27:01.067 --> 00:27:03.567
un dort iz antlofn, farshteystu, der

00:27:03.567 --> 00:27:06.687
kapo, eyner iz antlofn. m'hot tsugenumen ⟨dem⟩ uniform bay di nakht

00:27:06.687 --> 00:27:08.807
dem OBERLAGERFUHRER

00:27:08.807 --> 00:27:12.393
farshteystu, hot ongetun zayne kleyder, iz er antlofn. m'hot ⟨nokhet⟩ undz geyogt

00:27:12.393 --> 00:27:13.443
farshteystu

00:27:13.443 --> 00:27:16.063
un m'hot geshosn a por man undzere far bekhinem

00:27:16.063 --> 00:27:17.793
UNK kurts tsu di zakh

00:27:17.793 --> 00:27:19.743
bin ikh dort ongekumen keyn MAUTHAUSEN

00:27:19.743 --> 00:27:23.992
hob ikh getrofn dem, hot er gevolt di zupe, bin ikh tsuganen tsu dem WALTER, dem OBERKAPO

00:27:23.992 --> 00:27:25.142
zog ikh "WALTER

00:27:25.142 --> 00:27:26.042
gib mir

00:27:26.042 --> 00:27:28.417
gib mir a zupe far dem, ⟨mayn⟩. er ⟨zitst⟩ krank."

00:27:28.417 --> 00:27:30.650
zogt er tsun im, "er hot a goldenem tson nokh.

00:27:30.876 --> 00:27:32.490
rays im aroys dem tson."

00:27:33.036 --> 00:27:34.687
iz der zun tsugegangen

00:27:34.687 --> 00:27:35.867
der zun, er iz do do

00:27:35.867 --> 00:27:37.187
a bilyarder

00:27:37.187 --> 00:27:38.787
hot aroysgerisn di tson

00:27:38.787 --> 00:27:41.867
un gegebn dem WALTER un hot im gegebn a por zupn

00:27:41.867 --> 00:27:42.630
azoy UNK

00:27:42.630 --> 00:27:45.860
hot men dort geshrign vayter "vu, ver iz di fakhmener?"

00:27:45.860 --> 00:27:52.518
ot der kapo, UNK gevolt geyn, g- vu dort vu s'iz gut, hot men gevust hot men gezogt UNK "er iz a elektriker, der iz a dos"

00:27:52.518 --> 00:27:53.348
der tsveyter

00:27:53.348 --> 00:27:55.318
hot men undz geshikt avek fun dort

00:27:55.318 --> 00:27:56.998
durkh DORA

00:27:56.998 --> 00:27:59.754
DORA iz gevezn, m'hot geboyt VAU eyns

00:27:59.754 --> 00:28:00.891
VAU tsvey

00:28:01.335 --> 00:28:03.220
zenen mir gekumen keyn DORA

00:28:03.220 --> 00:28:05.920
DORA iz geven a s- groyser lager, oykh a toyte lager.

00:28:05.920 --> 00:28:07.609
m'hot gearbet ineveynik

00:28:07.609 --> 00:28:09.819
un di vos zey hobn gearbet in droysn bay di berg

00:28:09.819 --> 00:28:12.039
UNK gearbet in tuneln

00:28:12.039 --> 00:28:13.462
geven a toyter.

00:28:13.587 --> 00:28:15.794
vos hot pasirt? ikh g- dem

00:28:15.794 --> 00:28:16.908
⟨ZAWACKI⟩

00:28:16.908 --> 00:28:18.622
vos ikh hob dir dertseylt vos iz gevezn

00:28:18.622 --> 00:28:20.062
in

00:28:20.062 --> 00:28:21.022
BRESLAU

00:28:21.113 --> 00:28:22.339
GORLITZ

00:28:22.868 --> 00:28:26.345
der gantser UNK der UNK ⟨ZAWACKI⟩, der shrayber fun

00:28:26.345 --> 00:28:29.435
fun UNK fun VAU eyns, VAU tsvey in DORA

00:28:29.955 --> 00:28:32.239
bin arayngekumen ⟨tsu geyn⟩, hot men undz gegebn a numer

00:28:32.239 --> 00:28:34.249
ikh hob gekrign UNK mir gegebn a numer.

00:28:34.249 --> 00:28:36.219
host gekrign a numer fun di GORLITZ?

00:28:36.219 --> 00:28:37.686
ikh hob a numer fun GORLITZ.

00:28:37.686 --> 00:28:39.946
fun, vi heyst er, fun DORA.

00:28:39.946 --> 00:28:41.876
hob ikh gekrign dem numer fun DORA

00:28:41.876 --> 00:28:43.674
un er hot undz dort getrofn

00:28:43.674 --> 00:28:46.024
un m'hot dort geganen. ikh ⟨hob⟩ gevorn

00:28:46.024 --> 00:28:48.104
der forman.

00:28:48.906 --> 00:28:50.129
dort bin ikh gevorn

00:28:50.129 --> 00:28:51.099
der forman

00:28:51.099 --> 00:28:52.369
UNK fun ts-

00:28:52.369 --> 00:28:54.299
tsu boyen dem tramv- tsu UNK

00:28:54.299 --> 00:28:54.929
di

00:28:54.929 --> 00:28:57.164
aparatn vos geyt aroyf tsum

00:28:57.164 --> 00:28:59.454
tsu flign tsu nokh LONDON, tsu bombn LONDON

00:28:59.454 --> 00:29:00.514
on a mentshn.

00:29:00.514 --> 00:29:01.803
bin ikh dort gevorn.

00:29:01.803 --> 00:29:03.513
nor dort bin ikh gevezn.

00:29:03.705 --> 00:29:06.714
un dort bin ikh geshlofn in, in, a pritshe

00:29:06.714 --> 00:29:08.524
vos iz gelign a rus

00:29:08.524 --> 00:29:10.574
un ikh hob gekrign a gut hemd

00:29:10.574 --> 00:29:14.184
un ikh heyb mikh oy- er iz gel- ikh bin gelign azoy, un er iz gelign azoy.

00:29:14.184 --> 00:29:15.680
mayn hemd iz nishto.

00:29:16.615 --> 00:29:20.709
hot tsugenumen dos hemd, hot er mir avekgevorfn a farloyzt hemd. s'iz geven geferlekh LAUS.

00:29:21.458 --> 00:29:25.671
hob ikh nisht gevolt ontun dos hemd un aropgeyn tsu UNK. iz geganen der kapo dort fun dem tsimer

00:29:25.963 --> 00:29:27.983
un er hot mir es ge- UNK ⟨gegebn⟩

00:29:27.983 --> 00:29:29.803
tsvontsik oyfn ⟨ARSCH⟩

00:29:29.803 --> 00:29:32.043
hot mir aropgenumen kop arayn azoy

00:29:32.043 --> 00:29:33.973
un geshtanen, un er hot mir gegebn mit a shpadl

00:29:33.973 --> 00:29:35.313
hot mir gegebn dem ershtn

00:29:35.313 --> 00:29:36.919
bin ikh shoyn nisht gevezn keyn mentsh.

00:29:36.919 --> 00:29:38.509
shoyn nisht ge- veys nisht vifl ikh hob gekrign.

00:29:38.509 --> 00:29:39.542
ikh bin gelign.

00:29:39.852 --> 00:29:41.831
UNK eyn molt kumt a selektsye

00:29:41.831 --> 00:29:43.421
arayn in lager arayn

00:29:43.421 --> 00:29:46.211
a selektsye UNK selektsye. ver geyt mit mit di selektsye?

00:29:46.211 --> 00:29:47.351
der ⟨ZAWACKI⟩.

00:29:48.660 --> 00:29:51.877
"vos tustu do?" hob ikh im dertseylt

00:29:53.402 --> 00:29:54.630
hob ikh im dertseylt

00:29:54.630 --> 00:29:55.910
vos do tut zikh.

00:29:56.068 --> 00:29:58.658
⟨iz⟩ geganen, hot er mikh arayngenumen tsu zayn shtub arayn

00:29:58.658 --> 00:30:01.448
un dort bin ikh gelign a por tog, un ikh hob mikh oysgeheylt.

00:30:02.211 --> 00:30:02.992
shoyn.

00:30:02.992 --> 00:30:04.685
un gey vayter oyf mayn arbet.

00:30:04.708 --> 00:30:07.798
mit eyn molt brengt men tsu geyn a grupe

00:30:07.798 --> 00:30:12.388
vos zenen geven in Frankra- bay UNK nor mener

00:30:12.775 --> 00:30:14.996
efsher zibetsn akhtsn mentshn.

00:30:15.542 --> 00:30:18.860
un me teylt mir tsu di grupe azoy vi ikh, ikh ken

00:30:18.951 --> 00:30:20.964
farshteystu, v- d- a bisl daytsh

00:30:20.964 --> 00:30:22.775
un me teylt mir tsu di mentshn

00:30:23.288 --> 00:30:26.634
tsu mir, un azoy iz dos geven. dort iz geven UNK

00:30:26.634 --> 00:30:28.614
un UNK in di grupe

00:30:28.614 --> 00:30:30.754
un ikh bin geven zeyer

00:30:30.754 --> 00:30:31.905
⟨koved⟩ man.

00:30:32.637 --> 00:30:37.710
i- mit eyn molt UNK dort hot gedoyert a por vokhn, ikh veys, efsher tsvey monat knap

00:30:38.762 --> 00:30:41.945
iz me likvidirt dem lager.

00:30:42.289 --> 00:30:45.602
me shikt undz avek. hot me- yidn, yidn muzn aroysgeyn

00:30:45.602 --> 00:30:49.219
⟨ale tsum ersht⟩ yidn. iz geshtanen UNK ⟨ZAWACKI⟩

00:30:49.410 --> 00:30:51.142
UNK zogt er "du geyst nisht."

00:30:51.705 --> 00:30:55.934
bin ikh geven in lager. iz er gekumen arayn tsu mir in lag- in blok arayn, blok zibetsn

00:30:56.059 --> 00:30:57.574
un hot gezogt "du geyst nisht."

00:30:57.574 --> 00:31:00.356
di komande heyst ⟨ZAWACKI⟩, kenst dir forshteln

00:31:00.683 --> 00:31:02.793
di komande hundert un tsvontsik man

00:31:02.793 --> 00:31:04.783
heyst komando ⟨ZAWACKI⟩

00:31:04.935 --> 00:31:07.528
iz er arayngekumen tsu mir in blok arayn un hot gezogt

00:31:07.585 --> 00:31:09.874
"⟨BROLEK⟩, BRONISLAW, du geyst nisht.

00:31:10.183 --> 00:31:11.270
du blaybst."
